------------------------------------------------------------------------
r4976 | olivier.salaun | 2008-04-25 16:17:15 +0200 (Fri, 25 Apr 2008) | 2 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/Makefile.am
   M /trunk/configure.ac
   M /trunk/src/etc/script/sympa
   M /trunk/src/etc/script/sympa.generic

