r4601 | david.verdin | 2007-09-14 09:31:50 +0200 (Fri, 14 Sep 2007) | 6 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/src/Conf.pm
   A /trunk/src/etc/crawlers_detection.conf
   M /trunk/src/tools.pl
   M /trunk/wwsympa/SympaSession.pm
